            "title": "金價上升　現貨金升0.84%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">資金流入金市避險，加上美元下跌，都帶動金價向上。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20170226_FI_gold-price_FB_source-web_-4-1-1-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20170226_FI_gold-price_FB_source-web_-4-1-1-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">現貨金一度逼近每盎司2930美元，高見2929.52美元，收報2928.63美元，升0.84%，現報2931.47美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期金收市報每盎司2945.4美元，升幅0.6%或18.7元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國總統特朗普簽署總統備忘錄，表明要對每個向美國進口產品徵收關稅的國家徵收對等關稅，加劇市場對全球貿易的憂慮。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14704965-%e9%87%91%e5%83%b9%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%87%e3%80%80%e7%8f%be%e8%b2%a8%e9%87%91%e5%8d%870-84",
